---
title: Beef, Pork & Bacon Ragu Pie with Mushrooms, Mash Potato Topping & Red Wine Jus
description: A saucy beef pork and bacon ragu, it’s the lullaby our stomachs need to send us off to dreamland. Comforting and hearty, mixed with mushrooms and veggies in a red wine jus sauce, the filling will lull you into bliss and the mash potato topping is sure to fulfil all your pie dreams.
